DBEM - DataBase tools for Electron Microscopy


-------------
Requirements:
-------------
- Web server Apache
- MySQL (4.0 or higher)
- PHP (5.0.4 or higher) with MySQL, GD, Session, XML, MRC 
- JavaScript-enabled browser
- CSS-enabled browser


----------
Unpacking:
----------

Unpack the archive into your web server directory:
	$ cd /yourwwwdir
	$ tar zxvf dbem[version].tgz

--------------
Configuration:
--------------
	$ cd dbem

	$ cp config.php.template config.php

	- edit the file config.php
	- set your MySQL parameters:

	$DB_HOST	= "[SQL HOST]";
	$DB_USER	= "[SQL USER]";
	$DB_PASSWORD	= "[SQL PASS]";
	$DB		= "[database]";

	$ cd dbem/processing

	$ cp config_processing.php.template config_processing.php

	- edit the file config_processing.php

--------------
run:
--------------
	Go to http://yourhost/dbem/

